  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2003-04-01",
    "date": "2006-11-28T17:35:40Z",
    "text": "Religious Freedom Restoration Act - Amends the Federal judicial code to deny the district courts of the United States, Guam, the Virgin Islands, and the Northern Mariana Islands and the United States Court of Federal Claims jurisdiction to hear or determine any case in which any requirement, prohibition, or other provision relating to religious freedom that is contained in a State or Federal statute is at issue."
